description: Crispy toasted bread topped with a fresh mix of diced tomatoes, garlic, and basil, drizzled with olive oil. A perfect light appetizer.
Golden, crispy breaded mozzarella sticks served with a tangy marinara dipping sauce. Perfect for sharing or enjoying solo.
Spicy buffalo wings, crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside, served with a side of ranch dip to cool down the heat.
Baked mushrooms stuffed with a rich mix of cream cheese, garlic, and herbs, providing a delicious and savory bite.
Fresh mozzarella, cherry tomatoes, and basil on skewers with a balsamic drizzle. A refreshing starter.
Sautéed shrimp in garlic and butter, served with a lemon wedge for a burst of freshness.
Classic deviled eggs with a creamy yolk filling and a hint of paprika for spice.
Juicy mini meatballs in a marinara sauce, topped with fresh basil. A flavorful bite.
Warm spinach and artichoke dip served with toasted bread for dipping.
Crispy spring rolls filled with veggies and served with a tangy dipping sauce.
Tender and juicy grilled steak, perfectly seasoned, and served with a side of creamy mashed potatoes and sautéed vegetables.
Succulent grilled chicken breast seasoned with herbs, served with roasted vegetables and a light lemon butter sauce.
Classic Italian pasta with a rich and hearty meat sauce, topped with parmesan cheese and served with a side of garlic bread.
Perfectly grilled salmon fillet served with a tangy lemon butter sauce, accompanied by steamed vegetables and wild rice.
Assorted vegetables stir-fried in a light soy sauce with hints of ginger. Served with steamed rice.
Soft tortillas filled with seasoned beef, fresh lettuce, and pico de gallo, served with a side of salsa.
Grilled lamb chops seasoned with rosemary and served with mashed potatoes and green beans.
Pasta tossed with fresh vegetables in a light garlic and olive oil sauce.
Shrimp sautéed in garlic butter sauce served over linguine with fresh parsley.
Layers of pasta, cheese, and vegetables in a savory marinara sauce. A hearty vegetarian option.
Classic Coca-Cola served ice cold to refresh your palate.
Freshly squeezed lemonade with just the right balance of sweetness and tartness. Served over ice for ultimate refreshment.
Chilled iced tea brewed to perfection, served with a fresh lemon wedge.
Freshly squeezed orange juice with no added sugar. A naturally refreshing drink full of vitamin C.
Bubbly sparkling water with a refreshing taste. Perfect for pairing with any meal.
Strong and rich espresso with a bold taste. A classic pick-me-up.
Creamy latte with steamed milk and a shot of espresso. Perfect for any coffee lover.
Refreshing green tea brewed with care, providing a light and healthy beverage option.
Creamy milkshake available in chocolate, vanilla, or strawberry flavors. A treat for any sweet tooth.
Calming herbal tea with a mix of natural herbs for a soothing experience.
A slice of moist red velvet cake with a layer of rich cream cheese frosting.
Warm, gooey chocolate brownie with a crisp top and soft center. Perfect for chocolate lovers.
Classic cheesecake with a buttery graham cracker crust and a creamy filling.
Homemade apple pie with a flaky crust and cinnamon-spiced apple filling.
Smooth and creamy chocolate mousse topped with whipped cream and chocolate shavings.
Classic Italian tiramisu with layers of mascarpone and coffee-soaked ladyfingers.
Vanilla ice cream with chocolate sauce, whipped cream, and a cherry on top.
Delicate pastry tart filled with custard and topped with fresh seasonal fruits.
A delightful pie made with layers of banana, cream, and toffee on a graham cracker crust.
Italian dessert with a silky, smooth texture served with a berry sauce.
Classic crispy French fries served with a side of ketchup.
Sweet potato fries with a light seasoning, perfect for a healthier choice.
Freshly made coleslaw with cabbage, carrots, and a tangy dressing.
Creamy mashed potatoes, a comforting classic.
Baked potato with a crispy skin, served with butter and sour cream.
Grilled asparagus with a touch of olive oil and sea salt.
Toasted garlic bread with a crispy crust.
Assorted steamed vegetables, lightly seasoned.
Fresh corn on the cob, steamed and lightly salted.
Crispy onion rings served with a side of dipping sauce.
Fresh quinoa salad with cucumber, tomato, and a lemon dressing.
Oven-roasted cauliflower with a touch of garlic and olive oil.
Bell peppers stuffed with a seasoned rice and vegetable mixture.
Zucchini spirals served with a light marinara sauce.
Grilled Portobello mushrooms with a balsamic glaze.
Crispy kale chips seasoned with sea salt.
Zucchini slices baked to perfection with a light seasoning.
Fresh avocado salad with tomatoes, onions, and a lime dressing.
Creamy chia seed pudding with coconut milk and a hint of vanilla.
Grilled chicken served on a bed of mixed greens, perfect for a light and healthy meal.
